  "title": "HEAD BAKER",
  "description": "<p><!--td {border: 1px solid #cccccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></p><p>Responsible to produce a full range of breads and cakes using the company’s recipe specifications.</p><p>Always observe and adhere to the standards of safety and hygiene for production, kitchen and culinary work area.</p><p>Ensure maintenance and sanitize baking utensils, tools and machinery.</p><p>Experience of handling bakery equipment.</p><p>Able to lead and supervise a team of bakers to ensure smooth daily operations.</p><p>Passion for baking and a strong commitment to delivering consistent quality.</p><p>Willingness to work night shift and split shift.</p><p>Willingness to work extra hours or weekend if needed.</p>",
